{"tid":1243487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會趁亂審議明日大嶼","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T16:12:47.000Z","uid":36470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09aff9f17119ae4cf1ece8d9b7a2a296a6d97b61","tid":1243487,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"究竟香港人仲有冇未來？<br />\n<br />\nSource： <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190616/20705404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F20705404&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu9jJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=fa917f81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F20705404&h=e804584d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190616/20705404</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隨着特首林鄭月娥無限期暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，立法會下周一、二原本安排的大會已取消，周三則如常舉行大會，但有人注意到下一個爭議項目或許已悄然冒起。<br />\n<br />\n上周三起連續未有召開大會的立法會主席梁君彥透過發言人回應，相信當局是認真聽取各界人士及市民的聲音，終作出暫緩修例的決定，認為有關安排可以讓各方冷靜，並讓當局多就法案解說，呼籲議員重新聚焦議會事務，包括審議其他法案，監察政府及審批撥款等。下周三的大會議程，暫時只列出兩項無約束力的議員議案，分別是民主黨林卓廷提出的加強打擊水貨活動議案、收緊內地人來港安排議案，及自由黨張宇人提出有關制訂輸入非本地培訓醫生新機制的議案，未見有政府法案。<br />\n<br />\n土地正義聯盟斥打尖<br />\n但有市民注意到，周五財務委員會會議上的唯一議程涉及林鄭提出的「明日大嶼」填海計劃，有關中部水域人工島相關研究的撥款申請。土地正義聯盟認為政府「趁機博亂」審議填海撥款，將東大嶼打尖上6月21日的財委會，斥林鄭一邊暫緩修例，一邊硬闖爭議法案。<br />\n<br />\n$5.5億研明日大嶼張建宗促早通過- 晴報- 港聞- 新聞- D190401<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/.../$5.5億研明日大嶼%20張建宗促早通過\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F...%2F%245.5%E5%84%84%E7%A0%94%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%2520%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E4%BF%83%E6%97%A9%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu9jJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=6396feee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/.../$5.5億研明日大嶼%20張建宗促早通過</a><br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼可能喺香港史上最大嘅歷史騙局<br />\n<strong>所謂歷史上的最大騙局，當然不是單指資金規模的龐大，而是整個規劃概念如何葬送掉一整代人的未來。</strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC-%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%96%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%98%85%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2596%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2598%2585%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu9jJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=82b07d55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2596%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2598%2585%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580%2F&h=80315913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC-%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%96%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%98%85%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80/</a>"},{"pid":"00391a5b746c5901f29b3f572c7081a873dc82cb","tid":1243487,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"更正： 押後左 但唔係取消。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波稱明日大嶼研究撥款申請於財會改為最後一項<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%BC%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A0%85-110411660.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E9%25A0%2585-110411660.html&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu9jJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=1b17ae96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%BC%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A0%85-110411660.html</a><br />\n<br />\n財委會主席陳健波表示，鑑於政府見到近日的議會氣氛，明日大嶼計劃的相關研究撥款申請，原本由議程的第三項調至最後一項，有可能難以在今個立法會期內通過。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，明日大嶼相關研究撥款申請調至最後，一定有助緩和社會現時的緊張形勢，認為政府這個考慮正確。大量的民生項目，涉及約760億元，已經準備好待審批，希望利用會議時間盡量多批出項目，對整個社會都有益。"},{"pid":"639b6aa20c826ce833fa9e65789e77fdf26b7aa5","tid":1243487,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c163623a22f904ec5ad41dd842c20be5f0dcf67","tid":1243487,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"依單又係影響幾代人。。。"},{"pid":"88dbc27ea96f48ed6307594b8c2bd3924c051a85","tid":1243487,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"即係21 都有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依家無人理，個個為d number食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab0f02f287dfc8274e8630f6fec8688f481ccf8","tid":1243487,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88dbc27ea96f48ed6307594b8c2bd3924c051a85","tid":1243487,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"即係21 都有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依家無人理，個個為d number食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hk